abstract: >
  Reproduction package for "Auditable denominator design for patent field delineation: A WBS-ITC codebook-plus-ledger approach".
  Contains the released adjudicated dataset, family-domain decision ledger,
  machine-readable WBS-ITC codebook, descriptive query provenance, and
  scripts for downstream regeneration of the core body tables
  (main analytical accounting and rule-to-adjudicated diagnostic outputs), body figures (Figs. 2, 3, 4), and Online Resource 1
  quantitative diagnostics (Tables S6a, S8, S9, S10, S13, the numeric
  components of Table S12, Table S14 within-layer comparison of
  deterministic first-pass and adjudicated mapping outputs, Table S16
  expanded within-layer benchmarking against deterministic and restrictive
  delineation variants, and Fig. S1) reported in the manuscript. Also
  includes scripts/build_audit_sample.py and scripts/score_audit.py
  supporting the Table S15 reviewer-executable blind audit protocol; no
  author-internal audit results are reported in the manuscript.
  Interpretive keyword summaries in Table S12 are documented but not
  script-generated. MANIFEST.md provides the expected reference values
  for verification of the regenerated outputs.
